        {
          "text": "We are located in Roșia Montana, Carpathian Mountains, Transylvania, an area with mountains, valleys and lakes, but also with a rich culture and history because of the heritage built by various civilizations that came here since antiquity to extract gold. We offer guided tours and there are 4 marked tracks that starts from the front of our house."
        },
